product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:17:## 2. Base Reward
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:18:Every completed 10-question Mini Game Attempt has a base reward:
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:20:| Completed Action | Base Reward |
