product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:25:- Applies whether the Attempt is passed or failed.
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:27:- Once the user confirms the 100 reward, that Attempt cannot later receive retroactive x2.
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:32:| Action | Final Reward | Insight Outcome |
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:34:| `รับ 100 ค่าประสบการณ์` | 100 | Remains locked |
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:41:- Secondary button: `รับ 100 ค่าประสบการณ์`
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:43:When the immediate Rewarded Ad completes successfully:
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:50:## 4. Claiming 100 Then Opening Locked Insight
