product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:52:- Set `final_reward = 100`.
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:67:- Final reward remains `100`.
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:75:After successful Rewarded Ad completion:
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:88:## 7. Failed Attempt Reward Rule
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:89:The same reward and Insight unlock choices apply to failed Attempts.
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:94:## 8. Rewarded Ad Failure / Cancellation
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:95:If an optional Rewarded Ad fails, is interrupted, or is not completed:
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:101:## 9. Reward Outcome Matrix
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:102:| Situation | Final Reward | Insight |
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:104:| Free User accepts base reward | 100 | Locked |
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:106:| Free User accepts 100 then unlocks from current Locked screen | 100 | Permanently unlocked |
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:108:| External entitlement opens Insight | Reward determined by selected reward action | Permanently unlocked |
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:110:## 10. Required Reward Data
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:113:| `base_reward` | `100` |
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:114:| `final_reward` | `100` or `200` |
