product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:124:- Accepting 100 finalizes reward value for that Attempt.
product_bible/02_reward_system/mini_game_reward_logic.md:125:- Insight may still be unlocked after accepting 100, but x2 is not granted retroactively.
