product_bible/03_vip_and_subscription/vip_subscription_logic.md:17:- A completed Mini Game Attempt's Insight opens immediately without an unlock advertisement.
product_bible/03_vip_and_subscription/vip_subscription_logic.md:19:- Insight unlocked while VIP is active remains permanently unlocked after VIP ends.
product_bible/03_vip_and_subscription/vip_subscription_logic.md:20:- VIP does not automatically grant unlimited x2 ค่าประสบการณ์.
