product_bible/03_vip_and_subscription/vip_subscription_logic.md:58:| VIP Reward | 0 |
product_bible/03_vip_and_subscription/vip_subscription_logic.md:59:| Active VIP Subscription | 10 per paid billing cycle |
product_bible/03_vip_and_subscription/vip_subscription_logic.md:62:An active paid VIP Subscription user may use 1 Ticket immediately after completing a Mini Game Attempt to change the reward from 100 to 200 ค่าประสบการณ์ without watching an ad.
