product_bible/01_game_flow/mini_game_flow.md:121:## 6. Daily Soft Reward Decay
product_bible/01_game_flow/mini_game_flow.md:123:Mini Game supports a daily soft reward decay for Free Users who continue playing without choosing the rewarded-ad option.
product_bible/01_game_flow/mini_game_flow.md:127:- Let Free Users continue playing Mini Game without a hard block.
