product_bible/01_game_flow/mini_game_flow.md:194:- Never hide basic result information behind an advertisement, VIP prompt, or Insight lock.
product_bible/01_game_flow/mini_game_flow.md:198:- Reward actions are supplied and validated by `mini_game_reward_logic.md`.
